Package: tquery
Type: Package
Title: Temporal Query Language for Event-Level Health Data
Version: 0.2.6
Author: Hans Olav Melberg [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Hans Olav Melberg <hans.melberg@gmail.com>
Description: A port of the Python tquery library: a temporal query
    language for event-level health register data. Lets you answer
    questions like "K50 before K51" or "min 3 of J01* inside 100 days"
    over data.table-style event logs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    data.table (>= 1.14)
Suggests:
    jsonlite,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
